    "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nTemporary workaround until FlashInfer fixes TRTLLM attention on SM103 (flashinfer-ai/flashinfer#2939). TRTLLM attention auto-selection is now gated on exact SM100 instead of the SM10X family. SM100 is unaffected and continues using TRTLLM attention as before.\r\n\r\nFixes #21904",
